title: Logs
body:
Hey!

So I just downloaded this again after months of not having something to game on, and I get this error that pops up saying "Unspecified error occured. Please check the logs for more information" I've tried redownloading this a few times and nada, just the same issue. Anyone got any idea how to fix this?

replies.body: At what percent are you receiving that error?  That can help determine the origin of the issue.  Let me know!
After rebooting my computer suddenly that error has shown up to me as well please help me i can't handle  without League and my friends do not know solution for this problem.
I've actually downloaded everything and am attempting to open it when it pops up, the only thing I don't have downloaded is any updates that may have been added due to the game not opening.
